<p>Eligibility criteria, guidelines and application form can be downloaded from <em>
<a href="http://www.britishcouncil.in/study-uk/scholarships/commonwealth-scholarships">http://www.britishcouncil.in/study-uk/scholarships/commonwealth-scholarships</a>
</em></p>
<p>Last date for applying online in the Ministry: <strong>16th September, 2016 (till 3:00 PM)</strong></p>
<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
